nodes.bodyText: Actually, this can happen, and might be what's happening here. There is no PCollection for this tag, but the user outputted a value to this tag. It would make sense to record this output even if we didn't use it. This is another downside of attaching these counters to PCollections themselves rather than to PTransform outputs.
